{"id": "ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 594, "displayName": {"text": "U :Dessert Story", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5eExVUmFablY1V1ZwcVNFUmxTalEwUzNBMGJGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "I came with friends for dessert one evening, but it was a bit disappointing overall.\nWhen we arrived (a little late), all the toast items were already sold out. The staff didn’t inform us beforehand and just let us sit down, which felt quite unprofessional.\n\nThe regular cakes were average — nothing special. The shaved ice (bingsu)was less sweet than I expected, which was actually a good thing for me, but it was served in very basic, low-quality dishes that didn’t match the café’s supposed aesthetic or price level.\n\nThe biggest disappointment was the Thai Tea Mille Crepe. The sauce was not smooth at all — it had clumps and felt very sweet(looks like curry?). I still finished it, but the next day I suffered from severe diarrhea. I strongly suspect the sauce and cream in the Thai Tea mille crepe were not fresh.\n\nLesson learned: it’s probably best to avoid dairy-based desserts here in the evening.\nWill think twice before returning.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came with friends for dessert one evening, but it was a bit disappointing overall.\nWhen we arrived (a little late), all the toast items were already sold out. The staff didn’t inform us beforehand and just let us sit down, which felt quite unprofessional.\n\nThe regular cakes were average — nothing special. The shaved ice (bingsu)was less sweet than I expected, which was actually a good thing for me, but it was served in very basic, low-quality dishes that didn’t match the café’s supposed aesthetic or price level.\n\nThe biggest disappointment was the Thai Tea Mille Crepe. The sauce was not smooth at all — it had clumps and felt very sweet(looks like curry?). I still finished it, but the next day I suffered from severe diarrhea. I strongly suspect the sauce and cream in the Thai Tea mille crepe were not fresh.\n\nLesson learned: it’s probably best to avoid dairy-based desserts here in the evening.\nWill think twice before returning.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "kiki Wong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100882927491440099225/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8qPvNIFt3D04x4Hr2UIgUzg_taFCxVtNbxpSXT3aY6z5awj8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-27T04:30:01.093547150Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5eExVUmFablY1V1ZwcVNFUmxTalEwUzNBMGJGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5eExVUmFablY1V1ZwcVNFUmxTalEwUzNBMGJGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xRVdVMWtPRFJRWDJaNFVsRkVZMk5KY1dONFUyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We came here for dessert and we got the ube milk with boba and the thai tea crepe cake. The ube milk had a great flavor and this was some of the softest boba I have ever had, which I really enjoyed. The crepe had a great thai tea flavor and it was moist. I am excited to come back and try more of the crepe cakes!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We came here for dessert and we got the ube milk with boba and the thai tea crepe cake. The ube milk had a great flavor and this was some of the softest boba I have ever had, which I really enjoyed. The crepe had a great thai tea flavor and it was moist. I am excited to come back and try more of the crepe cakes!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nuria Escriva", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102734018037285051373/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBhUsrv5fs1zsL7U5tlvl1Es42llRgyo3NFrqreb0zV0ybHupX=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-27T02:13:52.473309783Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xRVdVMWtPRFJRWDJaNFVsRkVZMk5KY1dONFUyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xRVdVMWtPRFJRWDJaNFVsRkVZMk5KY1dONFUyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveGNUQk1ORWxEZW1kM2NXWndWRVk1V0ZveVFVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Attentive service, great ambiance/vibes. Cant believe it’s open until 1am some nights!  I’ve only tried the mango sticky rice Bingsu, which was good, but I didn’t realize how big it was! Definitely could share between 2-4 people.  Main reason I won’t be able to come back often is the high price point. Our desserts were more expensive than our dinner earlier that night.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Attentive service, great ambiance/vibes. Cant believe it’s open until 1am some nights!  I’ve only tried the mango sticky rice Bingsu, which was good, but I didn’t realize how big it was! Definitely could share between 2-4 people.  Main reason I won’t be able to come back often is the high price point. Our desserts were more expensive than our dinner earlier that night.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "TTColibrí", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118044563161383941859/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9_yFJ0qj3IHjForDKy62mjso46o4Z9EbJA9-xx_ncfXOygw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-01T18:55:24.289273161Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveGNUQk1ORWxEZW1kM2NXWndWRVk1V0ZveVFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveGNUQk1ORWxEZW1kM2NXWndWRVk1V0ZveVFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5elVHWlBNa0ZLTTI5eVRrRTNUR1Z3UmpGWmJFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I visit this spot every time I want to treat myself after completing a stressful semester. Every time I get the mango sticky rice toast and it’s absolute perfection! It comes with a side of pandan coconut sticky rice and mango sauce, but I always ask for the coconut sauce instead because the coconut sauce is better, and traditionally mango with sticky rice is served with the coconut sauce, not mango sauce. I tried deviating for my usual once, and I ordered the salted egg yolk toast and I wasn’t impressed. 4 stars because it is pricey, and the mango sticky rice toast should be served with coconut sauce.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I visit this spot every time I want to treat myself after completing a stressful semester. Every time I get the mango sticky rice toast and it’s absolute perfection! It comes with a side of pandan coconut sticky rice and mango sauce, but I always ask for the coconut sauce instead because the coconut sauce is better, and traditionally mango with sticky rice is served with the coconut sauce, not mango sauce. I tried deviating for my usual once, and I ordered the salted egg yolk toast and I wasn’t impressed. 4 stars because it is pricey, and the mango sticky rice toast should be served with coconut sauce.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Caitlin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102755869470392970693/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlKbI_sEiaodvFfxtpaKiOzrrbjxJAdB7Y83zmwyLA_nZUV2E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-26T06:16:34.732606539Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5elVHWlBNa0ZLTTI5eVRrRTNUR1Z3UmpGWmJFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5elVHWlBNa0ZLTTI5eVRrRTNUR1Z3UmpGWmJFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJNlphS3ZnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Today, I had a wonderful time with my friends! We indulged in some delicious treats, including Honey Brick Toast for $20.00, Tempura Shrimp for $13.00, Cheese Fries for $14.00, and a refreshing Thai Tea drink for $6.50 with lite ice. We also tried a delightful Fired Boba Brown Sugar for $7.50 and ended our meal with Mango Sticky Rice Bingsu for $22.00.\nAlthough the place was a bit bustling, we made the most of it by sitting at the counter. Sharing our food was a little tricky, but we managed just fine! The restaurant, while small, was beautifully decorated and exuded a cozy atmosphere that made our experience even more enjoyable. It was definitely worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Today, I had a wonderful time with my friends! We indulged in some delicious treats, including Honey Brick Toast for $20.00, Tempura Shrimp for $13.00, Cheese Fries for $14.00, and a refreshing Thai Tea drink for $6.50 with lite ice. We also tried a delightful Fired Boba Brown Sugar for $7.50 and ended our meal with Mango Sticky Rice Bingsu for $22.00.\nAlthough the place was a bit bustling, we made the most of it by sitting at the counter. Sharing our food was a little tricky, but we managed just fine! The restaurant, while small, was beautifully decorated and exuded a cozy atmosphere that made our experience even more enjoyable. It was definitely worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "ahkwai Lert", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107597462103316142932/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWfk0KSPnUofMa0mLFI_rIYGy1H83UetLuk22ZpjemWzhqYg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-04-03T06:15:05.001964Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJNlphS3ZnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJNlphS3ZnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/photos/AWCwydjXDasIkuXzUfwXVZxvDxvqrHQ6xnb-R8mPLh_JHw0gzcE9jwdhXeiLDkoLJhlvwgemi6NX_SNH8jG82cob1vwcHOfvsSauufZ8pqXp0yD_O-RisQEDFQyfh1seIgK83aRJ2YvnnSLS1hchl5bbTIsrX9_B02Zdf3png3Ju9UmpmtAH8b1rH2NV8sBXmxHhgDUb1dCVl_5spgHeIinRAnJ0qAKPN1_VmV14eTykTDpiYAnMGqQNua5R2tlxdi2IZ46hhn7e8Vvfps1GtpRaZ-YAIsB1WM5KGM2DUk_E2tFdoikcvqOCeXA575qsj_oRmRj17QbC3enMEEqGwNUb7EsWEjYaULljS7epKW7a4UTBVkGUxlIlAB-YKh4wm0GTc6emAsuiztgy8R9n37qcXdonhLpxIPDgi_FcBfVWCrQ1OQ", "widthPx": 1440, "heightPx": 1152, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "U :Dessert Story", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/105218134065982739834", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbXt2Hk4s3xh81Oa31W7Li9u7mmTVmm9x7UfbGQ7D0U5r2ww=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC8j6rRaw&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC8j6rRaw!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80857f0bc2fa54b3:0x92b95255dbd47ab5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs1T6wgt_hYARtXrU21VSuZI/photos/AWCwydhL7U1mowgrT3TkyffTIYJmj6JZwSDAZQxaU8gbe_PAqBJDhq5rpMpjV7H5AIxeJBZlkWx8TvkIWfoRlyLBtAuI8DM1EJEs_aM_n8ve8ZhkG76b6Mm962eSbGouacgmHGN1CiOhtDSTVJerb7rPeZBL5FO8__uXXI2MOoX5ViFeALTNCv